{"tid":374603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連登巴打們有冇野想問台妹? 入黎! 你問佢答!~","createTime":"2017-08-26T01:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T05:28:58.000Z","uid":1006,"like":2,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f382a97e230b9ea41a8d1e012cfe6bd1e0e65712","tid":374603,"uid":1006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"我兩年前去台灣旅行果時聽演唱會識左個台灣女仔 (連登仔最愛既大波台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n之後當時佢帶住我係台灣玩左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n大家幾傾得埋就加左facebook 交換埋contact <br />\n<br />\n咁岩佢呢幾日會黎香港玩 我做翻佢導遊+柴可夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家係機場等緊接佢機 一陣我會畀部手機佢同連登巴打玩你問佢答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢睇得明少少香港用語 但係如果認真問野最好盡量用書面語 <br />\n同埋唔該唔好玩野問淫野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (雖然佢好玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n預計大約9點半左右接到佢機 有興趣既可以諗定有乜想問先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb731ceeb3d039785376d1073bdc445c4d8e2d1","tid":374603,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:15:43.000Z","msg":"點睇香港男仔?<br />\n有冇拍拖? 無既可唔可以認識下佢?"},{"pid":"8a5cf1a76cbbf8ff64037fda998a7ef365726c1a","tid":374603,"uid":1006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:16:44.000Z","msg":"係喎btw,<br />\n台灣人手機打字係用開注音定拼音多<br />\n差d唔記得佢地好似唔係用速成"},{"pid":"1052bf975dc94e566942b9a74bc9e7c78ac38558","tid":374603,"uid":40470,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩山長水遠來香港玩你問我答？"},{"pid":"b3a9b2d091d5cbed705032bdec82480f3824d9f8","tid":374603,"uid":8771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:17:02.000Z","msg":"我好多台灣女仔朋友都好喜歡香港人 加油 大家"},{"pid":"473c30f55417e77dd604363